<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1' />
    <link
      rel='icon'
      type='image/x-icon'
      href='https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/monster-graffio.svg'
    />
    <link
      href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
      rel='stylesheet'
      integrity='sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM'
      crossorigin='anonymous'
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='card text-center'>
      <div class='card-header'>
        Featured
        <a class='navbar-brand' href='#'>
          <img
            src='https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/monster-graffio.svg'
            width='30'
            height='30'
            alt=''
          />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class='card-body'>
        <h5 class='card-title'>Dear {{name}}</h5>
        <p class='card-text'>Welcome to our platform! We are thrilled to have
          you join our community and embark on an exciting journey with us.
          Whether you're a seasoned user or new to this space, we're here to
          provide you with an exceptional experience. Our platform is designed
          to cater to your needs, offering a wide range of features and
          resources to help you achieve your goals. From insightful articles and
          interactive forums to personalized recommendations and expert
          guidance, we strive to empower you every step of the way. Get ready to
          connect, learn, and grow with like-minded individuals who share your
          passion. Thank you for choosing us, and we can't wait to see what
          incredible experiences await you on our platform!</p>
      </div>
      <div class='card-footer text-body-secondary'>
        <p class='card-text'>Best regards</p>
        <p class='card-text'>Jobster</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
